Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:21.22,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:26.85,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.69,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.79,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:50.17,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.05,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.66,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.86,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:20.91,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.95,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.48,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe such a thing is really feasible?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, \NI believe this is what Munakata would've wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, theoretically \Nnothing should prevent you from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, Oka have lived and trained for this day only. \NI can't stress this enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been through a lot, \Nbut Oka has always remained loyal to this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, more than ever, \Nthe time for her to master this technique is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we've already secured our positions in the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen's Cup '90 for all of us is to become our first \Nand foremost, tangible, full-scale challenge to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Posed by Oka, by me, and finally...\NBy Munakata as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.05,Default,SIGN,0,0,80,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0.55)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\3a&H2D&\fscx144\fscy136}Episode 9\N\N\N\NQueen's Cup '90                       \h\N\h                                               Begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to the tonight's party, Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One unusual foreign player should also come, \Nwhose participation, I believe, will surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Unusual player?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days before the deadline, the "last minute application" \Ncame from a player whom I couldn't help but to recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, we'll meet her on the venue. \NLooking forward to seeing her if so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to beg for the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No peeping in a present before it is gifted to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A present? \NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:42.80,Default,SIGN,0,0,1,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Queen's Cup '90 Championship Opening Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Soviet player Sinyachova!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, from Hungary, Chan Seska!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,West German player, Henkel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for coming. \NAlso, the mass media of all kinds are welcomed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, the Queen's Cup '90 \Nopening party is considered open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, are you feeling victorious today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this is the first time I'm attending such a grand party. \NEverything here is luxury embodiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, look here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one we saw in the video, Gene Ryder. \NAnd she is the darkness itself today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her special trademark - \Nto always dress in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She swore to wear no clothes of other colours \Nuntil she becomes the Wimbledon champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wimbledon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a sign of her solid determination \Nto achieve her dream and never lose grasp on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, the Spaniard Marchesa Broir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd of suits surrounding her \Nis her coaching staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of them has signed an expensive contract \Nwith her parents, being paid $100,000 per year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the top-notch coaches here. \NProbably...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Back and forth, she is the only person in the world \Nto carry this variety of her personal coaches along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentleman!\NLet's begin the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,1,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Queen's Cup Opening Party Venue
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The highlight of the evening! \NQueen's Cup '90 matchups intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me present you with the \Nmatching schedule for the first Queen's Cup stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry on the verge. Last minute application \Nis so much like Midorikawa. But you're here after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. \NMeans I did it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Hiromi, how've you been?\NDoing fine now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a surprise it is! \NI couldn't even imagine seeing you in this tournament too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the prize money. \NThis tournament is an expensive one. Couldn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you a pro now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, once and for all. Got a pro tournament licence. \NAn American one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Madame Butterfly? \NFinally giving up on your noble pupa tennis to become a pro-imago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps... I'm thinking of buying myself \Na new Mercedes for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit!\NLaughing it off like the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so strained, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. I still have a long way to go. \NI was rather brought here by inertia, attracted by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it is ought to upset him, \NI will never... be able to quit... tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings, dear Todo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Queen's Cup '90 \Nfirst round matchups have finally been announced.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out, mine's the third match \Nof the very first day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morita Kyoko \Nwill be my first opponent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems to me like Ms. Morita \Nis very different from myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Middle-aged veteran pro \Nwith five years of pro experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She used to be an exchange student in Australia once \Nand during that time she became a pro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, Oka. The difference between you and Morita \Nwill stand out apparent in the upcoming match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't think that it'll lie in abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.63,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This match outcome will be decided \Nby your concentration and determination only.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll depend on how can you concentrate on your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,However, your self-confidence is no less important. \NAnd the best indicator to that will be the points' ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent is a pro. And for the sake of your future, \Nyou should also fall ill with a pro-obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,While on the court, \Ntry to be everything at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.75,0:08:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see something \Nthat absorbed you completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie!\NI also saw who is on the eighteenth court.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's shape seems greater than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,During this whole morning... \NDuring the morning they only took three short breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.36,0:08:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, \Nthese two were endlessly practising her grand strokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing else?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me like Oka and Daigo right now \Nare taking some completely new step forward together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether she's already ripe for the next stage or not - \Nthe Queen's Cup '90 is bound to make apparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What in your mind are these two \Nmight be trying to pull off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika, just like you always did before, \Nyou must now stick to your own path, regardless of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must've got into me, \Nthat made me lose sight of it for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The present me has nearly forgotten \Neverything that my father taught me ever since I was so little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hiromi suddenly grows up in front of me, \NI must also grow up and catch up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,To climb the highest peak, \NI should fly higher than the peak itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I capable of flying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do better than this! \NTry harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing should scare you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Midorikawa's match, however, is the first one of the first day \Nof the first round. Her opponent is an American player Smith.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While Madame Butterfly, as well as Ryder, will play \Nwith the the first match winner. The same goes for Broir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of the seeding, \Nthey won't enter the contest until round two. Meaning...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's just one more reason, Todo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For me and Midorikawa \Nto get through the first round whatever the cost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cause' we won't ever share court with Madame Butterfly \Nand other promising players otherwise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For us to be reunited again, \NI must defeat Morita by all means.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I know for sure is \Nthis time any repêchage match is no longer an option for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,First round, first match. Midorikawa Ranko playing \Nagainst Irene Smith. The match is starting any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it!\NSouthpaw's renewed cannon serve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stunning game! \NThis is a truly impressive comeback by Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She successfully overcome her right hand crisis, \Nthat almost made Midorikawa retire on the health basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After turning into a southpaw, \Nshe returned to the court with a resounding success!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In continuation to the first set, \Nin the second set she also has the significant lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ozaki listening. \NWhy, look who's calling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've got it. \NMidorikawa is playing her first match right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity... \NWhy can't they rebroadcast it to Los Angeles as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo? That fellow must be still practising at the club. \NHaven't returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's match is the third one of today's. \NBy the time it's over, it'll be way past midnight where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter. Anytime, whatever the outcome is, let us know. \NTodo is all out of patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa just served such a dazzling ace! \NShe is truly incredible, what a fabulous revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A flawless play... \NMatch point already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right, this is the first round for me. \NNow to secure the lead, and the victory is mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryuzaki Reika, Oka Hiromi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our rivalry has always been \Nthe greatest honour for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The very reason behind my return to the court \Nis acquiring a taste for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Game over.\NMatch won by Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,1,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond this point \Nthe audience is not allowed to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Authorized staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The second match \Nis only on "Play ball" stage, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Want something of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Melon pie, fried chestnuts, \Nice, supermarket spicy chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hiromi's favourite snacks to your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. \NBut after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,After?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... \NOka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Morita.\NNice to meet you today and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm Oka. \NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you've been in Australia all this time, right? \NI'm not familiar with Japan's amateurs. Barely know a few ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I was too busy settling things with sponsors, \Nso I couldn't attend the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I'm seeing your face for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You here, using a fairly heavy racket, you know. \NHow arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let yourself be provoked, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This person is one of the few Japanese pros presented in rankings. \NAnd she ain't cheating her usual style today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite having mediocre abilities, she is the type of pro \Nwho wins with her mouth rather than her play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are welcome to change my mind - come out on the court \Nand show how well can you hit the ball, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost. And don't you dare to try tricking my friends \Nwith your pathetic performances again. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburger... may I have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, do your best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be watching you from the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\iclip(353,311.615,594,473)}Then, I'll be watching you from the stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the long-awaited third match \Nof the first round begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In this match we're gonna give it a try and see \Nif our practices helped you to advance to a new stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But have I already mastered it enough \Nto bet on it in the actual game?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You will do it. \NWe will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it.\NYou're the only one who can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The first round was great.\NCongratulations on your triumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, they are about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Service is Oka's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she winning? \NWhat is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. Instead, you'd better hurry to bed. \NDon't you have an important match tomorrow yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me clarify, are you defying the advice \Nof your free yet so competent manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka, I have faith in you. \NAnd in your victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... In you doing your best \Nand showing everyone a wonderful match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Out! 0-40!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected, her techniques are well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet she's still nothing but an amateur.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One shot, one shot, \Nshe's not willing to hit any balls except the desired ones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This one's mine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Out! \NGame won by Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Zounds!\NWhat an unfortunate miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fault! It's a double fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So far, Oka is making it a service-game, \Nreaching the break already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Every minute the fact becomes more apparent, \Nthat Oka is not trying her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,While the score is in favour of Morita, \Nwho is constantly securing the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,One can even say, Morita allows herself to savour the victory, \Nas Oka's power is being masterfully dodged by her all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the moment my match has begun, he was staying there \Nsilently all the time, not even approaching the stands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coach... What's that supposed to mean? \NWhat are you trying to tell me by suddenly turning your back on me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though during our practices \Nit took effect sometimes,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when you do so in a real match, \NI may not be able to handle it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it for sure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm definitely gonna miss the timing a little \Nand will then have to wait for another shot chance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, this match... \NI will lose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it, Oka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Try it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Must hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By yourself, Oka. \NYou can do it this way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait though... If I let it continue this way, \Nlosing is really a matter of time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,15-all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was... \Nthat shot right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka is doing some kind of double hits now, \Nalmost as if she'd become more than one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey? What happened there, Ozaki? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible... This is the first time I'm seeing \Nsuch an incredible kind of Oka's tennis!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's what one-side match is called indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No telling which one is a real pro now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi is very successful in adapting to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, albeit at first she hesitates, in the end she always \Nreturns to the ball, which she lost sight of for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi and coach Katsura have really taken this huge, \Ncompletely new step this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time they were not afraid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is just... \NUnbelievable!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,6-3, 6-0. Set count: two against one.\NMatch won by Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen's Cup '90 is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.58,0:23:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's growing hotter by day here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But unbelievable things happen at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the Midorikawa's struggle for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Although her opponent is some 14-years-old pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, despite all the reasoning, \Nuses her right hand again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep fighting, Midorikawa! \NAfter that round, you'll face Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:24:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: \N"Challenger Ranko!"